---
title: Nan's Veggie Mince & Parmesan Spaghetti Bolognese with Garden Salad & Flaked Almonds
description: Golden ropes of spaghetti coated in a rich, creamy tomato sauce and veggie mince. Finished with a scattering of almonds, Parmesan cheese
and a complementary salad, this is nothing short of a small bite of heaven.
